{
  "stem": "4247.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there was no income coming in at the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to pay 100 pengo for our rent, which was a, a very big obligation each month.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To give you an idea, 200 pengo was the ideal monthly income, right?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were songs made out of that, that whoever earns 200 pengo can, can joke and live quite easily, right?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Out of this 200 pengo, which a modest-- which a family modestly required, we paid $100 for our rent.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the other $100, which my mother very [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] frugally has converted into food and other issues, issues, socks, occasional clothing line.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most of them, however, said that's good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Tomorrow I get that, that house next door, right, which is the most natural, human, greedy reaction.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because humans are greedy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the general Hungarian [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] reaction by the-- by the-- by the populace.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, I, I have to-- I have to-- I have to perhaps go in a more chronological order because then I come back to, to, to your question, right?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Germans came in, right, in-- on the 19th of March, '44.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From then on, events started to roll very quickly, right?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was all organized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans knew exactly what they have done in, in Belgium and Holland and France and Austria.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a-- it was a module they have to put in place, and which they did very, very well.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know that, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My impressions of the time?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Things, events were, were happening so quickly that I didn't know where to turn, right?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had no time to, to, to, to develop impressions.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My personal impression, my instinctive impression was that there is going to be-- we'll have a horrible end.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
